OL,3,CPremier League club Everton launch
OL,4,Cappeal against latest points deduction
OL,6,Fhave formally lodged an appeal against
OL,7,Fthe two-point penalty imposed on the
OL,8,Fclub earlier this month for
OL,10,FThe Toffees indicated their intention
OL,11,Fto appeal last Monday, the same day
OL,12,Fthe sanction was announced. ITV News
OL,13,Funderstands the appeal has now been
OL,14,Flodged.
OL,16,FThe club admitted breaching the
OL,17,FPremier League's profitability and
OL,18,Fsustainability rules (PSR) for
OL,19,Fpermitted losses by #16.6million for
OL,20,Fthe assessment period ending with the
OL,21,F2022-23 season.
