OL,6,FThe independent commission which
OL,7,Fimposed the sanction disclosed in the
OL,8,Fwritten reasons for its decision that
OL,9,Fthe Premier League had initially
OL,10,Fsought a five-point penalty.
OL,12,FThis was reduced to two by the
OL,13,Fcommission, after mitigation was taken
OL,14,Finto account, notably the fact that
OL,15,Fthe club were being punished twice in
OL,16,Fthe same overlapping period. In
OL,17,FFebruary Everton had a 10-point
OL,18,Fpenalty for an earlier PSR breach
OL,19,Freduced to six on appeal.
