OL,6,FEverton will now be aiming to achieve
OL,7,Fa further reduction to the two-point
OL,8,Fpenalty via the latest appeal.
OL,10,FEverton and Nottingham Forest have
OL,11,Fboth now appealed against the
OL,12,Fsanctions imposed on them, and the
OL,13,Fhope for all concerned will be that
OL,14,Fboth outcomes are known heading into
OL,15,Fthe final round of Premier League
OL,16,Fmatches on May 19.
