OL,6,FThe commission which issued the two-
OL,7,Fpoint penalty will also hold a
OL,8,Fseparate hearing to settle a dispute
OL,9,Fbetween the club and the league around
OL,10,Fcosts which Everton contend are
OL,11,Fassociated to the construction of
OL,12,Ftheir new stadium at Bramley-Moore
OL,13,FDock.
OL,15,FThis dispute is not covered by the new
OL,16,F'standard directions' for dealing with
OL,17,FPSR cases before the end of the season
OL,18,Fin which clubs are charged, so any
OL,19,Fsanction imposed would almost
OL,20,Fcertainly apply next season.
